      <text>They're supposed to be IC boards, for use to let others know about your
presence in the different towns, and for people to keep abreast of the
things going on ICly in said towns.  For example, if you were to come ICly
to Ebou Dar, you could post on this board that you're in town looking for
RP or something, or post some event that's going on in the city.    
</text>
