    <message>
      <header>An Official Decree</header>
      <slot>4</slot>
      <level>196</level>
      <author>235636</author>
      <date>1053704211</date>
      <authorname>Aaron</authorname>
      <text>*Penned in a flowing script on bleach white parchment*

Citizens of Ebou Dar,
     The last vestiges of the resistant against the Seanchan forces have
been eradicated.  The city is now under the complete control of the Empress,
may she live forever.  The Ever Victorious Army patrolls the streets at all
hours, day and night.  Any civil unrest will be met with swift justice.  Any
one entering the city, and all occupants within, must agree to swear the three
oaths, and all horses must be surrendered to the Army immediately.  Trade
will be restricted to Oath takers only, and all goods entering or leaving the
city must be checked at a Gate Post.
     Any information regarding the whereabouts of rebels or marath'damane must
be given to an Officer of the Deathwatch Guard or Ever Victorious Army.  Any
person found harboring such individuals will forfeit all property to the Empress
and suffer a public flogging or execution by beheading.

  Signed in my hand,
     Captain Aaron, Gardener, Deathwatch Guard
</text>
    </message>
