      <authorname>Garn</authorname>
      <text>*A broad sheet of parchment is pinned to the board by a heavy-bladed dagger*

Citizens of Ebou Dar!
    Know that these foreign scum who now patrol your streets shall not rest
easy in their occupation, or live long on the shores of our land!  As long
as we draw breath, the true Children of Altara will defy these cowardly
inavders, and that soon we shall triumph, and free the land from their foul
domination!  We shall send them to their graves, or they shall take their
foul monsters, and flee back across the sea where they belong!  Down with
the Shadow!  Freedom from the Tyrants!  Long Live Altara!
</text>
    </message>
