Citizens of Altara,
     This city is now a province of the Seanchan Empire.
Any attempts to resist the will of the Empress, may she 
live forever, or any other Blood or military personel will
result in immediate arrest and a fine of 100 crowns.  A
second arrest will result in death under the charge of
treason.
     Information that helps lead to the arrest of any 
rebel who has committed crimes against the Empress, may
she live forever, will receive a 200 crown reward.
All riots or acts of treason will be put down with
force.

  Signed,
     Captain Aaron son of Garen of the Deathwatch Guard
</text>
